value.0: Live bate generaly used for fishing.  Its slightly more effective than just a hook but its genearly used quickly.

An expensive lure.  Those fish wont even know what got them.  The best lure gold can buy.  This lure is hand carved, painted, and is perfectly balenced able to easily fool almost any fish.  It would be a shame to loose it though.
A fly, general used for fishing.  Its more effective than live bait and can be reused as many times as you like, just dont get it caught in the weeds.

A peice of leather that when placed over a peice of wood or similar material to make a crude archery target.
